NAME
       lvmdbusd â€” LVM D-Bus daemon

SYNOPSIS
       lvmdbusd [--debug] [--udev]

DESCRIPTION
       lvmdbusd is a service which provides a D-Bus API to the logical volume manager (LVM).  Run lvmdbusd(8) as root.

OPTIONS
       --debug Enable debug statements

       --udev  Use udev events to trigger updates

SEE ALSO
       dbus-send(1), lvm(8)

